ActExcise Act, 2001
PrecisREGULATIONS RELIEVING SPECIAL DUTY ON CERTAIN TOBACCO PRODUCTS which allow certain tobacco products and cigarette brands to be prescribed for the purposes of potentially allowing them full exemption from the special duty provisions on exported tobacco products, and take effect on July 1, 2003.
